{"tid":1566750,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"成面暗瘡問題","createTime":"2019-09-13T17:22:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-18T12:06:26.000Z","uid":221836,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"176310250f13fcfa143032765a6672f8681be7e8","tid":1566750,"uid":221836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T17:22:40.000Z","msg":"最近的起心肝想改善下暗瘡問題<br />\n利伸成面暗瘡都有四五年咁耐 生完好返又會再生<br />\n冇停過 好返嘅又會有印 E五年日復日咁生 就嚟爛面 面上有紅印又有凹凸印<br />\n個人變得好自卑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔敢拍拖<br />\n我每日起身會洗一次面 夜晚沖涼會洗一次面 洗面會用洗面奶 用嘅係日本PAIR  個隻洗面奶<br />\n有時都會用PAIR個隻暗瘡膏搽下 但都冇咩用<br />\n試過唔同款牌子嘅暗瘡膏都冇用 只係暗瘡會&quot;謝&quot; 但之後又生返 我都會用下蘆薈膏搽下<br />\n曾經聽人講唔用洗面奶會好啲 我都試過 但反而情況仲差 塊面油到會仲差過用洗面奶個時 係咁生暗瘡😭😭😭😭<br />\n我都好想好似其他女仔咁 有靚皮膚 皮光肉滑<br />\n明明自己父母冇E啲問題 點解我有 <br />\n有冇人可以推介下有咩皮膚科醫生好 醫到暗瘡？<br />\n價錢可能唔好咁貴 學生未有咁多錢賺到 可以睇到咁多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d39bdb60e74499111151ebc7fa9b2ac500f9f9ca","tid":1566750,"uid":201414,"like":1,"dislike":37,"score":-36,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T17:26:03.000Z","msg":"已經想像樓主塊面應該有多火山 莫講話見到 想像到都唔多開胃<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 行房時最好笠住頭為你另一半着想<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8739ef1e3cb95f534240553ace595edb54d85f14","tid":1566750,"uid":69472,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"quote":{"pid":"d39bdb60e74499111151ebc7fa9b2ac500f9f9ca","tid":1566750,"uid":201414,"like":1,"dislike":37,"score":-36,"citedBy":