1566750,"uid":149849,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T18:34:42.000Z","msg":"睇緊方慶生，食緊a酸，1500一個月<br />\nso far食左一個月，成效未明，但好多巴絲推薦，因為價錢都算fair<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/devil.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b740aa2856c961e3119acf6ee25f3cdbba105797","tid":1566750,"uid":258731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T18:36:33.000Z","msg":"【終極核彈】《願榮光》之後－成立海外臨時民主政府<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1566796\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1566796</a><br />\n<br />\n《願榮光》之後。。。<br />\n天滅中共 平反六四！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">海外臨時政府 自由香港<br />\nFREE HONG KONG</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/freehongkonghkg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ffreehongkonghkg&d=sKkpDxzP%2F%2Fasg9kKOzx88p1QB7Ma9ovE6nvZW%2BRTqP4%3D&h=4a8b028e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/freehongkonghkg</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/nBMTNBB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnBMTNBB.jpg&h=16392072&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n讓這攬炒旗隨風飄揚！（logo已獲攬炒巴授權使用）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>人哋北韓都做到 香港唔係做唔到呀嘛？</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n中共已經決定企硬，連溫和到咁既五大訴求都唔會接受。咁呢個政府仲有咩面代表人民<br />\n<br />\n擇個好日子揀個好地方，設立海外臨時政府<br />\n<br />\n目標係「要使國際社會廣泛相信港共政府為非法政權，爭取外國政府支持，替天行道，天滅中共」<br />\n「因應警察濫用暴力+濫捕事件於國際組織上追究」<br />\n<br />\n最後「推動香港進入real autonomy 嘅時代」<br />\n<br />\n因為而家我哋已經無嘢可以好輸，如果我哋就咁俾場運動完結，最後受害，被批鬥，被清算係每一個真。香港人。前線於是，和理非也如是。警察已經將文革係各中小學重演，唔駛好耐就會到其他界別。"},{"pid":"0c1824d5ea2cc46e94b699545fd8b6bf94a1941f","tid":1566750,"uid":30834,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T19:31:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"664d837f9584e09857ef86a531025965fffb231c","tid":1566750,"uid":293603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T19:46:12.000Z","msg":"你試下轉氨基酸洗面 <br />\n同埋暗倉膏用耐左會無效 唔知係咪有抗藥性<br />\n所以唔可以長用一隻架"},{"pid":"22bd903272e9b3aa6f324f72ccd4ab56189997ed","tid":1566750,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2ec3a5add248b786c9951141a02deb8d05a1d0e6","tid":1566750,"uid":194483,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T18:29:57.000Z","msg":"用果酸嘅洗面，護膚<br />\n萬寧，屈臣氏有賣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T14:07:16.000Z","msg":"Brand name?"},{"pid":"f9f0087719015ec288338cfdb1f8dabc2381dd3f","tid":1566750,"uid":198412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T21:55:42.000Z","msg":"天水圍天瑞 陳嵐峯<br />\n佢係基督徒 會平一半比學生 又好人"},{"pid":"0adb7035e2bf7db4899468928e6c063411e70aca","tid":1566750,"uid":198412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f9f0087719015ec288338cfdb1f8dabc2381dd3f","tid":1566750,"uid":198412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T21:55:42.000Z","msg":"天水圍天瑞 陳嵐峯<br />\n佢係基督徒 會平一半比學生 又好人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T21:56:39.000Z","msg":"I mean 食a酸 我勁後悔唔早啲食唔洗留疤"},{"pid":"1e11aeb38aa3e95315dc24c697d3e05f9c9a737d","tid":1566750,"uid":217683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T22:06:04.000Z","msg":"戒糖戒奶"},{"pid":"f587860ccd0cad85a4e8fd63493386357427f21d","tid":1566750,"uid":194483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"22bd903272e9b3aa6f324f72ccd4ab56189997ed","tid":1566750,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2ec3a5add248b786c9951141a02deb8d05a1d0e6","tid":1566750,"uid":194483,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score"