有你一樣暗瘡問題！ <br />\n以前食過一個療程A酸，好翻左。 <br />\n但最近幾個月又突然爛臉。之後走左去睇中醫！飲左幾碗覺得有好到！ <br />\n可以考慮下中醫！ 調理下身體！"},{"pid":"77aa025e5f1c04476fd49c61c5cacf8bf77ecb64","tid":1566750,"uid":63037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T15:22:20.000Z","msg":"有冇食過抗生素個d？<br />\n如果想包好就食a酸"},{"pid":"01b61137f326bac50d7f0167639e565abf8f306d","tid":1566750,"uid":202282,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T15:31:06.000Z","msg":"治本：有耐性既建議睇中醫<br />\n等唔會再生新既暗瘡<br />\n舊既印甚至凹凸洞可以去美容院做微針"},{"pid":"2525d2a9a44b35b69051734af7c62bcf146a8e80","tid":1566750,"uid":127347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T15:38:03.000Z","msg":"A酸啦 我都食緊就黎一個月，暫時未見效果，係油真係收左，瘡照爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"030836ddcca01d4d0b6378d63f76754512a618b8","tid":1566750,"uid":38165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T15:49:21.000Z","msg":"A酸啦 我都食緊 嚴重既就無其中方法<br />\n捱得過a酸你就重生"},{"pid":"e96cdfdc8ba669ee91a32d08d70b12ce3d945c8b","tid":1566750,"uid":141456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T02:35:36.000Z","msg":"做下食物敏感測試先"},{"pid":"1be3c857f30c2296e761da0d51e076303a9d5c99","tid":1566750,"uid":239106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T02:38:21.000Z","msg":"去睇皮膚科醫生.我係中環睇.<br />\n醫生幾好唔會亂叫你食a酸或者茶"},{"pid":"9d936a637b3d8b3d2befcd8e50827c294b25472a","tid":1566750,"uid":165339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T02:40:23.000Z","msg":"真係要睇醫生呀，呢d已經係病嚟，唔好諗住慳呢舊錢"},{"pid":"85c9cf7bd50274d74493beb15f03dd359c974ef3","tid":1566750,"uid":274732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T02:42:36.000Z","msg":"食小啲糖 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a193a357c54db96a7bb57af7f9df911777512688","tid":1566750,"uid":140726,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T02:44:10.000Z","msg":"做左20年人一粒暗瘡都冇<br />\n飲品儘量少甜，少凍飲<br />\n戒牛<br />\n戒朱古力 &lt;- 好重要<br />\n一定要勤洗面，我自己齋用清水洗，一日碼洗4-5次"},{"pid":"03d221bed960cf79f1b7256d4a75f212e73e84d7","tid":1566750,"uid":166474,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T02:50:26.000Z","msg":"介甜,介夜訓,多飲湯水，只用清水洗面，用紙巾印乾塊面(毛巾有可能積聚油脂同細菌)，一個月後一定有改善<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90f576af0b155736c13d4fb1ccfc481ec83b2a2c","tid":1566750,"uid":202889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T02:51:58.000Z","msg":"咁凹凸洞點搞？"},{"pid":"08d73a5c82a4c3cfc2d41c99ad86f58d0250e5a2","tid":1566750,"uid":63392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T03:03:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"744f056087e30b7e7fabda5c3fb4db75bbef1d84","tid":1566750,"uid":53406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T03:11:34.000Z","msg":"冇暗瘡，面油多又點搞？<br />\n利申男"},{"pid":"982cd7de500e466c7d3368c8ed52f3a18e8d7612","tid":1566750,"uid":132461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T03:12:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1. 戒糖<br />\n<del>2. 繼續keep住用洗面膚日夜洗面</del><br />\n3. 狂飲水<br />\n<del>4. 睇醫生 因為暗瘡始終同內分泌有關</del></blockquote>"},{"pid":"ea99d739b57ff00fa0076f883b8b329fbfa144b8","tid":1566750,"uid":130271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T03:13:30.000Z","msg":"都係啊酸㗎喇<br />\n因為a 酸可以縮小毛孔內負責油脂分泌嘅gland<br />\n直接解決暗瘡成因 (油脂分泌過多)<br />\n<br />\n如果唔計睇醫生 只是藥的價錢，要視乎你嘅體重<br />\n因為a酸係按體重食藥的，同埋成個療程係有個固定嘅份量。<br />\n所以如果你係男，想省錢的話，可以只睇三四次醫生，當醫生幫你驗左幾次血，證明你個肝可以承受a酸，就可以同醫生講byebye，直接問藥房佬買藥。<br />\n<br />\n不過如果你係女就建議要持續睇醫生，因為a酸好影響女性荷爾蒙，有機會會影響生育，孕婦食A酸會流產就係咁解<br />\n<br />\n過來人 成功由暗瘡毒撚變成只係毒撚 希望幫到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d10521fed7325303b8a7b72a466354ba65231fbe","tid":1566750,"uid":106879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T03:17:59.000Z","msg":"食咗3次療程抗生素 又黎料 成臉暗瘡 今個星期六打算去睇醫生 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f9be0ee81e56c667f6b56e2d87bfe058b4bdd7d","tid":1566750,"uid":314021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T03:18:00.000Z","msg":"<strong></strong>食藥 我中六個期都係咁 成塊面日日都生幾粒 生親都有印 仲要又紅引大撻 d瘡又腫又紅又大粒 真係冇一忽係正常 塊面望落去就係紅色一大撻一大撻咁樣 <br />\n<strong></strong>之後去左睇醫生 食左年半a酸 收左面油 再之後間唔時爆發 後尾頂唔順 keep住食doxycycline 依家冇咩暗瘡同埋清左好多印 變返正常<br />\n <strong></strong>希望幫到你 我以前d瘡多到真係個個人都望撚住我塊面 加油呀樓主你 撑住"},{"pid":"49067c1522dd16de23724c90ae43aab55538be5a","tid":1566750,"uid":314021,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9f9be0ee81e56c667f6b56e2d87bfe058b4bdd7d","tid":1566750,"uid":314021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T03:18:00.000Z","msg":"<strong></strong>食藥 我中六個期